  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the clinical efficacy of the extended release formulation of tacrolimus
      (Advagraf®) in patients with severe atopic dermatitis, who can not be treated adequately with
      cyclosporine A because of side effects and/or non-responsiveness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
